blurt 1.0 ShowPostCategory.pm
===========================

A plugin for blurt 1.0 that displays the category of the current post and the url
of this category in story templates.

By Matthijs de Jonge (rhmtts@gmail.com).

This software is public domain software: do with it whatever you want.


INSTALL:
========

- Upload ShowPostCategory.pm to the plugins directory of your blurt
  installation on the server

- Nothing else :-)

VARIABLES:
==========

The ShowPostCategory plugin supplies the following variables for use in all
templates:

$ShowPostCategory::Category : the name of the post category
$ShowPostCategory::Category : the url to the post category

both are empty if not applicable.
